<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-size:15pt; font-weight:600;">上线前准备</span></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">1.qwebbrowser优化</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">	a.\$\{</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">	b.html文件</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">	c.处理所有有问题的文档</p>
<p style="-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><br /></p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">2.跑任务模式的时候，如果problem或者content没有值会导致如下出错</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#cc7832;">def </span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#ffc66d;">format_string_for_run_javascript</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#a9b7c6;">(t_string):<br />    </span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#808080;"># \\`\\`\\`Python<br />    </span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#a9b7c6;">t_string = t_string.replace(</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#6a8759;">&quot;</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#cc7832;">\\\\</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#6a8759;">`</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#cc7832;">\\\\</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#6a8759;">`</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#cc7832;">\\\\</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#6a8759;">`&quot;</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#cc7832;">, </span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#6a8759;">&quot;```&quot;</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#a9b7c6;">)<br />    t_string = t_string.replace(</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#6a8759;">&quot;</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#cc7832;">\\</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#6a8759;">`</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#cc7832;">\\</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#6a8759;">`</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#cc7832;">\\</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#6a8759;">`&quot;</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#cc7832;">, </span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#6a8759;">&quot;```&quot;</span><span style=" font-family:'JetBrains Mono','monospace'; font-size:9.8pt; color:#a9b7c6;">)</span></p></body></html>